{
  "stem": "25651.7",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know, you asked me what the tasks were.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I went to a place called Canada.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why Canada?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because in Canada, everything was available, including hernia belts.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, because everything was taken out these thousands and thousands of people that were arriving every week.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And everything was sorted-- glasses, watches, jewelry, clothes, shoes, hernia belts.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was-- there was a big store of hernia belts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You'd be surprised how many people had a hernia and bring hernia belts into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyway, he goes out to the staff car.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I admire him how he jumps from one stone to the next.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He hardly gets his boots wet from the mud.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he's at the car and he bellows, laufer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So when you hear laufer, you have to run and report.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know, laufer [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I was told what to do.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I go and report.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he bellows something at me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I speak perfect German.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I understand German perfectly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But I was, like I told you, tsemisht after I had-- and I had enough presence of mind to run and salute and sort of say, I'm reporting for duty.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Actually, I was trying to do what he did, you know, jump from one stone to the next to avoid the mud.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I went right in the mud, but I continued running, you know, because he wanted me.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so that was it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You had to be-- instantaneous obedience was the sort of [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] way to behave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And you just had to copy what other prisoners did, you see?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he bellows some command.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I have no idea what he says.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, it's fatal to say, what?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You know, I beg your pardon?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
